OL,5, A woman with a rare condition which    
OL,6, threatens to crush her brain and spine 
OL,7, has undergone a fifth operation.       
OL,9,FMelanie Hartshorn, 33, of Cramlington, 
OL,10,FNorthumberland, has Ehlers-Danlos      
OL,11,Fsyndrome which causes her skull to     
OL,12,Fdislocate from her neck and spine.     
OL,14,FFor 18 months she wore a surgical halo 
OL,15,Fvest to keep her alive but that has now
OL,16,Fbeen removed by a surgeon in Barcelona.
OL,18,FMs Hartshorn is hoping to be home for  
OL,19,FChristmas, but will have to return to  
OL,20,FSpain in January for a final operation.
